{"article_id":"oeyivMZw5e0aZuwk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort pleaded guilty in federal court Friday as part of a plea agreement","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that involves cooperation with Special Counsel Robert Mueller","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and allows him to avoid a second trial .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"\" I plead guilty , ''","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Manafort , 69 , told U.S. District Judge Amy Berman in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Prosecutor Andrew Weissmann told the judge","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that Manafort 's deal includes a cooperation agreement with prosecutors ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"who are investigating","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"whether any Trump associates played a role in Russia 's meddling in the 2016 election .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"That could include interviews with prosecutors and testifying in court .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"A defense attorney for Manafort told Fox News","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"the deal includes `` full cooperation . ''","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"But the president 's team downplayed the significance of Manafort 's plea .","depth":3},{"id":13,"text":"\" Once again an investigation has concluded with a plea","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"having nothing","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to do with President Trump or the Trump campaign , ''","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Trump lawyer Rudy Giuliani said in a statement to Fox News .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"`` The reason :","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"the president did nothing wrong . ''","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders said Friday","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"that Manafort 's decision is `` totally unrelated '' to the president .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"Manafort , in a trial","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"set to begin Sept. 24 ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"had been facing seven counts of foreign lobbying violations and witness tampering in federal court in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"In August , in a separate trial in Virginia , a federal jury found Manafort guilty on eight counts of federal tax and banking crimes .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Manafort faces up to 10 years on these charges in Washington .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"He still faces sentencing for his guilty verdict in Virginia .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"As part of this agreement , Manafort has forfeited multiple bank accounts and several properties in New York .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"However , he will keep his properties in Florida and Virginia ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"where his family live .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Manafort attorney Kevin Downing told reporters","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"after the court hearing","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"it was a \" tough day \" for his client ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"\" who has accepted responsibility. \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Manafort \" wanted to make sure","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that his family was able to remain safe","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"and live a good life . \"","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"The case was brought by Mueller 's team ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"which is probing potential crimes","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"related to the 2016 election .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"But Manafort has not been charged with anything","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"related to the campaign .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"In August , Manafort ' s bank and tax fraud conviction made him the first campaign associate of Trump","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"found guilty by a jury as part of Mueller ' s probe .","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"\" I feel very badly for Paul Manafort , \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Trump told reporters after the August verdict ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that it had `` nothing to do with Russian collusion . ''","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"The president has called Mueller 's probe a `` witch hunt . ''","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Trump also said","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"he had \" such respect \" for Manafort","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"and called him a \" brave man. \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"In comments","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"interpreted to mean","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"he was open to pardoning Manafort ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Trump commended Manafort ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he \" refused to break \"","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and \" make up stories","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"in order to get a deal . \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"In the Virginia trial , prosecutors said","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Manafort hid income","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"earned from political work overseas","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"from the IRS","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"while fraudulently obtaining millions in bank loans .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Manafort had pleaded not guilty to all counts .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"The prosecution ' s star witness , Rick Gates","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"- Manafort ' s former business partner","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"who struck a plea deal","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"to cooperate with the government --","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"testified during the trial","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that he and Manafort committed bank and tax fraud together .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Downing , Manafort 's attorney , suggested after the guilty verdict in August","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that Manafort was open to striking a deal before the second trial .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"\" He is evaluating all of his options at this point , \"","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Downing said of Manafort .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":97,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":89,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":88,"right":12,"rela